verbose_text: For those who stayed on the regimen (M1 = 32; M2 = 22; M3 = 16), there was an increase in median domain scores for EF, OF, SD, IS, and OS over 3 months compared to baseline median scores but statistical significance was found only in the EF, IS, and OS median domain scores.
evidence: increase in median domain scores for EF, OF, SD
